	<a href="http://mashable.com/2015/10/20/benedict-cumberbatch-hamlet-live/">Mashable</a>，<a href="http://thirdrailrep.org/tag/of-mice-and-men/">thirdrailrep</a>，<a href="http://ameliareviews.wordpress.com/">Ameliareviews</a>，<a href="http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2013/04/06/the-queens-corgis-photos_n_3022346.html">HuffingtonPost</a>，<a href="http://www.huffingtonpost.co.uk/victoria-sadler/king-lear-national-theatre-review_b_4682065.html">Huffingtonpost
uk</a>，<a href="http://www.griffithcitycinemas.com.au/Movie/War-Horse-National-Theatre-Live">Griffith
City Cinemas</a>，<a href="http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-1377066/War-Horse-The-National-Theatre-triumphs-New-York.html">dailymail</a>，<a href="http://www.stageandcinema.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/Margaret-Thatcher-Haydn-Gwynne-and-Queen-Elizabeth-II-Helen-Mirren.jpg">StageandCinema</a>，<a href="http://movie.douban.com/celebrity/1031755/photo/1626108343/">豆瓣</a>，<a href="http://www.nytimes.com/2014/10/06/theater/the-curious-incident-of-the-dog-in-the-night-time-opens-on-broadway.html">New
